name: Sexy Hostess Uniform
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

Training settings:

35 images, 25 steps, 10 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.4-0.8

  • Keys: wearing sexy hostess uniform, inside airplane, airport

  • Adviced Image Size: 512x768

This model doesn't give what you expect if not used properly, my advice is to give a weight to the keyword "(wearing sexy hostess uniform:1.3)" like in the example, i had best results with weight 1.3.

Also the model is trained with many different uniform colors, so you might want to add ,COLOR uniform, like "a woman, (wearing sexy hostess uniform:1.3), red uniform,". You will not end with different colors uniforms but also with different types of uniforms.

As you can see in model images i have generated with many colors, take part of their prompts as example.

In the images listed i didn't think about hands, like using badhands5 so the hands are kinda wierd in most of the images. I just wanted to show the uniforms created by the model, the rest of the image can be prompted better.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
